  "faq": [
    {"q": "How does rickshaw advertising work?", "a": "We install LED screens and audio systems on auto rickshaws. Your ad plays while rickshaws move through busy Mumbra routes, reaching thousands of real viewers daily."},
    {"q": "What is the minimum campaign duration?", "a": "Minimum 7 days. We recommend 30 days for optimal brand recall and results."},
    {"q": "How do you track eye views?", "a": "GPS tracking + traffic density data + camera sensors. We calculate actual human eye views, not digital impressions."},
    {"q": "Can I choose specific zones?", "a": "Yes! Select from 12 zones across 4 strategic routes. Target exactly where your customers are."},
    {"q": "How soon can my campaign start?", "a": "Campaigns go live within 48 hours of booking and creative approval."},
    {"q": "What's included in the 30 free social creatives?", "a": "10 Instagram posts, 5 WhatsApp forwards, 5 Facebook posts, 5 Stories, 3 Carousels, 2 Reels - all branded for your business."},
    {"q": "Is there a booking fee?", "a": "No booking fee. Pay only for your campaign. Pricing starts at ₹1,238/day per rickshaw."},
